status-checker-heading: What is the Dependent Status Checker?
status-checker-content: The Dependent Status Checker is a tool that lets you check the status of your dependent's Canadian Dental Care Plan application.
online-status-heading: Who can check their dependent's application status online?
online-status-content: If you applied for the Canadian Dental Care Plan for your dependent, you can check their status online.
empty-status: The information you gave us doesn't match the information in our system.
